name: Creator of My Own Shit by Digvijay Pawar

metadata.name: Creator of My Own Shit #1/25
metadata.description:
Sometimes you need a little time alone, 
to rebuild yourself, to remember who you are 
An opportunity to reconnect —  
To pause, to breathe, to introspect.

In the end, you are the one capable of shaping your life;  
You — are the artist.
